quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  19,39,"Waanthirhum yawma alhasrati ithqudiya al-amru wahum fee ghaflatin wahum layu/minoon"
  19,40,"Inna nahnu narithu al-ardawaman AAalayha wa-ilayna yurjaAAoon"
  19,41,"Wathkur fee alkitabiibraheema innahu kana siddeeqan nabiyya"
  19,42,"Ith qala li-abeehi yaabati lima taAAbudu ma la yasmaAAu wala yubsiruwala yughnee AAanka shay-a"
  19,43,"Ya abati innee qad jaanee minaalAAilmi ma lam ya/tika fattabiAAnee ahdika siratansawiyya"
  19,44,"Ya abati la taAAbudi ashshaytanainna ashshaytana kana lirrahmaniAAasiyya"
  19,45,"Ya abati innee akhafu anyamassaka AAathabun mina arrahmanifatakoona lishshyatani waliyya"
  19,46,"Qala araghibun anta AAan alihateeya ibraheemu la-in lam tantahi laarjumannaka wahjurneemaliyya"
  19,47,"Qala salamun AAalaykasaastaghfiru laka rabbee innahu kana bee hafiyya"
  19,48,"WaaAAtazilukum wama tadAAoona mindooni Allahi waadAAoo rabbee AAasa allaakoona biduAAa-i rabbee shaqiyya"
  19,49,"Falamma iAAtazalahum wamayaAAbudoona min dooni Allahi wahabna lahu ishaqawayaAAqooba wakullan jaAAalna nabiyya"
  19,50,"Wawahabna lahum min rahmatinawajaAAalna lahum lisana sidqin AAaliyya"
  19,51,"Wathkur fee alkitabimoosa innahu kana mukhlasan wakanarasoolan nabiyya"
